<hr>
<dl>
  <dt> public final class <b>Notification</b>
  <dt> extends <a href="c2.framework.Message.html#_top_">Message</a>
</dl>
A component sends a notification whenever its internal state changes.  The
notification is meant to inform other components that are dependent on the
component. <p>
See the Message class for methods to add and remove parameters from
notifications. <p>
<dl>
    <dt> <b>See Also:</b>
    <dd> <a href="c2.framework.Message.html#_top_">Message</a>, <a href="c2.framework.Request.html#_top_">Request</a>
</dl>
